menu "LCD Blink Configuration"

    config LCD_BLINK_PERIOD_MS
        int "LCD blink period (ms)"
        range 10 3600000
        default 1000
        help
            Period in milliseconds for the LCD backlight blink cycle.
            One period consists of backlight ON (half period) and OFF (half period).
            For example, a value of 1000 means 500 ms on, 500 ms off.

endmenu
